-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-204_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bSqaIl iXTDAP pf-100_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-102_">Our Brand &amp; Production Ethics</span></h2><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-214_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-213_">As a brand and a manufacturer we are able to ensure that our brand ethics also apply on our production.</span></p><div data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion" class="sc-cNKqjZ diijrs pf-203_"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-172_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-146_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="dcc92925-10d1-4a57-a648-d6b44ef4fbb6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Safe Work Environment</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="dcc92925-10d1-4a57-a648-d6b44ef4fbb6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-171_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-170_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-169_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-149_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-148_">Our production studio in Lima, Peru is a safe work environment, keeping our workers protected from physical and mental harm. We make sure that in our studio there is:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-gHjyzD dQAIat pf-165_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-152_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-151_">No Child Labor</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-155_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-154_">No Unpaid Labor</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-158_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-157_">No Discrimination</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-161_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-160_">No Gender Inequality</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-164_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-163_">No Health Threats</span></li></ul><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-168_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-167_">Our founders actively participate in all stages of our work and are present daily in our production studio, looking for ways to improve and working hand in hand with our workers.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-181_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-174_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e1576e59-7da9-4cbc-83bc-7a3320ea626c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Wages</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e1576e59-7da9-4cbc-83bc-7a3320ea626c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-180_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-179_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-178_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-177_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-176_">We provide our workers with waves that are above the minimum wage standard in Peru. We aim to reward them with more benefits as soon as we become profitable.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-193_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-183_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="bc7a3320-ea62-4c62-930e-56377dd27869" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Gender Equality & Empowerment</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="bc7a3320-ea62-4c62-930e-56377dd27869" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-192_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-191_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-190_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-186_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-185_">At AYA, we accept workers of all genders. Our company consists of our founders, marketing team, art team, assistants, accountants and production workers. As of May 2022, we have 36 employees and freelancers working with us, 27 of whom are women.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-189_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-188_">Everyone at AYA can use their voice freely to disclose their opinions and ideas. They have a high level of autonomy in their day-to-day activities.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-202_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-195_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="7dd27869-2fb9-479c-bc8d-444cbe51ea65" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Racial Justice</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7dd27869-2fb9-479c-bc8d-444cbe51ea65" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-201_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-200_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-199_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-198_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-197_">AYA is an inclusive brand which is why nobody is discriminated for their nationality or color. Our team is formed of people of different ethnicities, who contribute to the company's development with their unique knowledge and perspective. Our employees and freelancers are from the United States, Latin America and Europe.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-216_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-iWBNLc NncQz pf-215_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/studioworker-1656962192536_1200x.jpg?v=1656962195" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/studioworker-1656962192536.jpg?v=1656962195 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9fb8" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-igXgud lhtyiH pf-81_ pf-bg-lazy"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-cjrPHo eOcrMz"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-82_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-134_ pf-bg-lazy pf-hide"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-83_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bSqaIl iXTDAP pf-84_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-86_">Our Goals</span></h2><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-87_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-89_">We made sure that from the start everything on our end is done legally and without causing any harm. But that is not where it ends for us. We aim to:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-gHjyzD dQAIat pf-90_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-91_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-93_"><b>Provide our people with more than living wages.</b><br>As soon as we become a profitable brand, we will upgrade our reward and benefit system to ensure all of our workers our happy in their work life, as well as in their private life.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-itWPBs dKPonY pf-94_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-96_"><b>Become inclusive to every-body.</b><br>We plan to add more sizes, gender neutral clothes, and one size fits all items so that everyone can buy sustainable clothes.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f9ac" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-igXgud lhtyiH pf-97_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-cjrPHo eOcrMz"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-98_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-99_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bSqaIl iXTDAP pf-209_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-208_">Our Suppliers</span></h2><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-103_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-105_">We plan to share information about our fabric and components suppliers as soon as we position ourselves on the market. At this moment, sharing everything about us could compromise the future of our business, but we give you our word that we use ethical practises in all stages of our production.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-106_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-108_">We take responsibility for our impact across the whole product lifecycle: impact on the environment, people and animals. We make sure that each part of our supply chain, from raw materials to product disposal, have zero to minimal impact on the environment and living beings.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-cbb3" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-igXgud lhtyiH pf-109_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-cjrPHo eOcrMz"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-110_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-218_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-iWBNLc NncQz pf-217_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/alpacas-1656962477528_1200x.jpeg?v=1656962480" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/alpacas-1656962477528.jpeg?v=1656962480 1536w" width="3000" height="2000" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-111_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bSqaIl iXTDAP pf-112_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-114_">Animal Rights</span></h2><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-118_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-120_">We do not use any fur, leather, down/feathers, angora, and exotic animal hairs and skins.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-115_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-117_">The only material of animal origin, that we are incorporating into our catalog in 2022, is Royal Alpaca Wool, sourced from small Peruvian co-op farmers. All alpacas are non-mulesed, receive regular medical care, and roam free in the highlands in the Andes Mountains.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>
